|[[File:Annular_Eclipse._Taken_from_Middlegate,_Nevada_on_May_20,_2012.jpg|x154px]][[File:Partial_solar_eclipse_Oct_23_2014_Minneapolis_5-36pm_Ruen1.png|x154px]]
